Package: rminions
Title: A Package for Easy R Processing Scalability Via Message Queues
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Jonathan", "Adams", email = "jd.adams16@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides generic functions to allow easy setup of worker servers
    in a distributed message-based computing environment for R. This environment uses Redis
    to handle communication with the worker servers via messages and PUB/SUB broadcasts.
    Functions are provided to facilitate the quick and easy setup of new servers for fast
    scalability.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.3)
Imports:
    jsonlite (>= 0.9.19),
    plyr (>= 1.8.3),
    rredis (>= 1.7.0),
    R.utils (>= 2.2.0)
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
